  "body": "After our review [#3292]of the [proposed spec](https://github.com/ConsenSysQuorum/IBFTDesign/blob/reference_tests/reference_tests/reftest_schema.json) we have identified the need to write a prototype to validate that we can write an test execution engine to meet the spec.\r\n\r\n**Acceptance Criteria**\r\n- The prototype should be able to read the `reftest_exN.json` files from [this repo](https://github.com/ConsenSysQuorum/IBFTDesign/tree/reference_tests/reference_tests) and successfully execute the tests.\r\n\r\n**Notes**\r\n\r\n- We might be able to leverage some of the code on the QBFT integration tests for this prototype.",
